   El Paso, Texas 222
   Elkhart-Goshen, Ind. 249
   Elmira, N.Y. 212
   Enid, Okla. 313
   Erie, Pa. 64
   Eugene-Springfield, Ore. 38
   Evansville, Ind. 207
   Fall River, Mass. 216
   Fargo-Moorhead, N.D.-Minn. 118
   Fayetteville, N.C. 306
   Fayetteville-Springdale, Ark. 129
