sessions after plans for a buyout ran into trouble.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks was
unchanged at 190.05. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was down .32 at 376.04.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 109.38 million shares with two
hours to go.
